1 + T(n/2) --> log(n)

1 + 2T(n/2) --> n

n + T(n/2) --> nlog(n)

n + 2T(n/2) --> n^2

   def f(n):
       if n <= 0:          --> O(n)
          return 
        1 + f(n-1)

