    if 2 function calls in single statement --> O(2^n) why?
       - because, from main :
                      - 1st call
                            |
                        ---------
                        |       |
                       call1   call2
    
                      ........
              it becomes -> 2^0 call --> 2^1 calls --> 2^2 calls .....--> 2^n calls


